flight.text: You know he's a flight risk.

flight.text: Hop a flight to Miami Beach.

translations.russian: Прыгают в самолет и летят в Майами.

flight.text: The family barely caught their flight.

flight.text: My daughter was on that flight!

translations.russian: Моя дочь была на том рейсе!
